snippet.title: Amber Heard announces the birth of her daughter
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is officially a mom. US actress Amber Heard arrives at the High Court for the libel trial by her former husband US actor Johnny Depp against News Group Newspapers (NGN) in London, on July 27, 2020. (DANIEL LEAL-OLIVAS/AFP via Getty Images)“I’m so excited to share this news with you. For years ago, I decided I wanted to have a child,” Heard said. “I wanted to do it on my own terms. I now appreciate how radical it is for us as women to think about one of the most fundamental parts of our destinies in this way. I hope we arrive at a point in which it’s normalized to not want a ring in order to have a crib.”Heard, who was at the center of the controversy during her divorce with actor Johnny Depp, added that she wishes to have some semblance of privacy, but said that because of her fame, she must “take control of this.”


All data is taken from the source: http://nydailynews.com
